N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6216.1 - Purpose of administrative complaint procedure

State Regulations

The purpose of this administrative complaint procedure is to
provide a uniform, nondiscriminatory administrative complaint procedure by
which any person who believes that there is a violation (including a violation
which has occurred or is occurring or is about to occur) of any provision of
title III of the Federal Help America Vote Act of 2002 (HAVA), may file a
complaint seeking redress of their grievance. Notes
